  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras/cfd14a347ada11b07cb5e41675b50fbb.poster.avif?t=1738139754\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras/cfd14a347ada11b07cb5e41675b50fbb.webm?t=1738139754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras/cfd14a347ada11b07cb5e41675b50fbb.mp4?t=1738139754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It's time to burn some calories and dish out some slaps!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shady humans, dim-witted mutant pigs, crazed knights, and more—all despise each other, but agree on one thing: making that hatred entertaining!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On the dusty ground of these devastated deserts, they invite you to join them in chaotic sports matches that’ll leave you scarred in less time than it takes to shout \"<strong>ROUGH RIVALS!</strong>\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras/d09ed3b50c1ec455e7e4be406018dfb4.poster.avif?t=1738139754\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras/d09ed3b50c1ec455e7e4be406018dfb4.webm?t=1738139754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras/d09ed3b50c1ec455e7e4be406018dfb4.mp4?t=1738139754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be brutal</strong>: Choose from a roster of 20 characters to send crushing blows. And if you’re more of a tactician — which we call “coward” here — opt for a technical game of dodging and passing to outplay your opponent!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be cunning</strong>: Between bouts of this chaos, organize your team, recruit and upgrade your players with a selection of 60 skills to create powerful synergies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be   brutal <u>AGAIN</u></strong>: Forget about justice, fair play, and the obscure rules of the ancient sport of American football. In the Scorched Wastes, there’s only one rule: bring the ball to the end zone and clear a path to get there!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras/2ab0f8f0ce12de98ed1a72ee8218b8e7.avif?t=1738139754\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras_big/2ab0f8f0ce12de98ed1a72ee8218b8e7.avif?t=1738139754 width=800 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge your friends in split-screen to relive the good old couch gaming days, and bully your loved ones in a game where no one really gets hurt!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Suit up and join us now!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras/cfd14a347ada11b07cb5e41675b50fbb.poster.avif?t=1738139754\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras/cfd14a347ada11b07cb5e41675b50fbb.webm?t=1738139754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras/cfd14a347ada11b07cb5e41675b50fbb.mp4?t=1738139754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It's time to burn some calories and dish out some slaps!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shady humans, dim-witted mutant pigs, crazed knights, and more—all despise each other, but agree on one thing: making that hatred entertaining!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On the dusty ground of these devastated deserts, they invite you to join them in chaotic sports matches that’ll leave you scarred in less time than it takes to shout \"<strong>ROUGH RIVALS!</strong>\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras/d09ed3b50c1ec455e7e4be406018dfb4.poster.avif?t=1738139754\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras/d09ed3b50c1ec455e7e4be406018dfb4.webm?t=1738139754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras/d09ed3b50c1ec455e7e4be406018dfb4.mp4?t=1738139754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be brutal</strong>: Choose from a roster of 20 characters to send crushing blows. And if you’re more of a tactician — which we call “coward” here — opt for a technical game of dodging and passing to outplay your opponent!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be cunning</strong>: Between bouts of this chaos, organize your team, recruit and upgrade your players with a selection of 60 skills to create powerful synergies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be   brutal <u>AGAIN</u></strong>: Forget about justice, fair play, and the obscure rules of the ancient sport of American football. In the Scorched Wastes, there’s only one rule: bring the ball to the end zone and clear a path to get there!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras/2ab0f8f0ce12de98ed1a72ee8218b8e7.avif?t=1738139754\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249490/extras_big/2ab0f8f0ce12de98ed1a72ee8218b8e7.avif?t=1738139754 width=800 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge your friends in split-screen to relive the good old couch gaming days, and bully your loved ones in a game where no one really gets hurt!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Suit up and join us now!</strong></p>",
